name: The development of the 'human world'
description:
You walk, you jump...

You see the world and how it'w going with a little weird way. The Egyptians, the town, trees dont exist anymore, they have been replaced forever. In the end everyone is dead!

ALSO IT TAKES A LITTLE MORE TIME TO LOAD

Small gameplay. I made it in a few hours with the help of my favourite 'Unity asset store'
